#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:855
msgid ""
"<b>Enable dark theme:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the system theme is asked to use a darker styling for the "
"application <i>(i.e. dark UI elements on bright text)</i>.\n"
"\n"
"Note that not all system themes provide such a darker variant, therefore "
"enabling this setting might not have an effect."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cumasaigh téama dorcha:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, iarrtar ar théama an chórais stíl níos dorcha a úsáid "
"don fheidhmchlár <i>(i.e. eilimintí dorcha UI ar théacs geal)</i>.\n"
"\n"
"Tabhair faoi deara nach soláthraíonn gach téama córais leagan níos dorcha "
"den sórt sin, dá bhrí sin ní fhéadfadh aon éifeacht a bheith ag an socrú seo "
"a chumasú."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:873
msgid ""
"<b>Enable client-side decorations:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search entry and main menu are displayed in the window title "
"bar.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, the main menu is displayed as a menu bar with the search entry "
"below it.\n"
"This resembles a more traditional UI layout and takes a little bit more "
"space."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cumasaigh maisiúcháin taobh an chliaint:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, taispeántar an iontráil chuardaigh agus an príomh-"
"roghchlár i mbarra teidil na fuinneoige.\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé díchumasaithe, taispeántar an príomh-roghchlár mar bharra "
"roghchláir leis an iontráil chuardaigh faoi.\n"
"Tá cuma níos traidisiúnta ar leagan amach chomhéadain úsáideora leis seo "
"agus tógann sé beagán níos mó spáis."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:893
msgid ""
"<b>Use binary units instead of decimal units:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This settings controls how file sizes are displayed.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Binary units:</b> This refers to binary IEC prefixes <i>(e.g. 1 KiB = "
"1024 bytes)</i>\n"
"\t• <b>Decimal  units:</b> This refers to decimal SI prefixes <i>(e.g. 1 kB "
"= 1000 bytes)</i>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Úsáid aonaid dhénártha in ionad aonaid dheachúlach:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Rialaíonn an socrú seo conas a thaispeántar méideanna comhad.\n"
"\n"
"• <b>Aonaid dhénártha:</b> Tagraíonn sé seo do réimíreanna dénártha IEC <i>"
"(m.sh. 1 KiB = 1024 beart)</i>\n"
"• <b>Aonaid dheachúlach:</b> Tagraíonn sé seo do réimíreanna dheachúlach SI "
"<i>(m.sh. 1 kB = 1000 beart)</i>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:913
msgid ""
"<b>Remember window size:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the window size from the previous session will be restored when "
"you open an FSearch window.\n"
"\n"
"Note that some window managers ignore this request and force the window to "
"have a different size."
msgstr ""
"<b>Meabhraigh méid na fuinneoige:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má chumasaítear é, athchóireofar méid na fuinneoige ón seisiún roimhe seo "
"nuair a osclaíonn tú fuinneog FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"Tabhair faoi deara go ndéanann roinnt bainisteoirí fuinneoige neamhaird den "
"iarratas seo agus go gcuireann siad iallach ar an bhfuinneog méid difriúil a "
"bheith aici."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:932
msgid ""
"<b>Behaviour after successfully opening a file:</b>\n"
"\n"
"When a file/folder was successfully opened one of the following actions can "
"be performed:\n"
"\t• <b>Nothing:</b> Nothing happens.\n"
"                        • <b>Minimize:</b> The currently selected FSearch "
"window becomes minimized.\n"
"\t• <b>Close:</b> Quit FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"You can configure if those actions should be triggered when the file was "
"opened with\n"
"\t• <b>keyboard shortcuts or menu entries</b> and/or\n"
"\t• <b>mouse click</b>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Iompar tar éis comhad a oscailt go rathúil:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Nuair a osclaíodh comhad/fillteán go rathúil, is féidir ceann de na "
"gníomhartha seo a leanas a dhéanamh:\n"
"\t• <b>Ní dhéanfaidh aon ní:</b> Ní tharlaíonn aon ní.\n"
"                        • <b>Íoslaghdaigh:</b> Íoslaghdaítear an fhuinneog "
"FSearch atá roghnaithe faoi láthair.\n"
"\t• <b>Dún:</b> Scoir FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir leat a chumrú an ndéanfar na gníomhartha sin a spreagadh nuair a "
"osclaítear an comhad le\n"
"\t• <b>aicearraí méarchláir nó iontrálacha roghchláir</b> agus/nó\n"
"\t• <b>cliceáil luiche</b>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:956
msgid ""
"<b>Show highlighted search terms:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search terms will be highlighted in the results view. For "
"example when you search for \"foo\" all appearances of <i>foo</i> in file/"
"folder names will be highlighted with bold characters:\n"
"\n"
"\t<b>foo</b>bar.txt\n"
"\tfile.<b>foo</b>\n"
"\n"
"This also works for regular expressions and wildcard expressions starting or "
"ending with an asterisk. "
msgstr ""
"<b>Taispeáin téarmaí cuardaigh aibhsithe:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má chumasaítear é, beidh na téarmaí cuardaigh aibhsithe sa radharc torthaí. "
"Mar shampla, nuair a chuardaíonn tú \"foo\", beidh gach cuma ar <i>foo</i> "
"in ainmneacha comhad/fillteán aibhsithe le carachtair throma:\n"
"\n"
"\t<b>foo</b>bar.txt\n"
"\tfile.<b>foo</b>\n"
"\n"
"Oibríonn sé seo freisin le haghaidh nathanna rialta agus nathanna fiáine a "
"thosaíonn nó a chríochnaíonn le réalta. "

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:978
msgid ""
"<b>Show tooltips:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the results view will show the full path of the focused file/"
"folder in a small tooltip window."
msgstr ""
"<b>Taispeáin leideanna uirlisí:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, taispeánfaidh an radharc torthaí cosán iomlán an "
"chomhaid/fhillteáin atá dírithe air i bhfuinneog bheag leideanna uirlisí."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:995
msgid ""
"<b>Show icons in name column:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, file/folder icons will be shown in the name column."
msgstr ""
"<b>Taispeáin deilbhíní sa cholún ainm:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, taispeánfar deilbhíní comhad/fillteán sa cholún ainm."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1012
msgid ""
"<b>Remember column configuration:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the column configuration of the results view from the previous "
"session will be restored when you open an FSearch window. This includes the "
"size and visibility of all columns."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuimhnigh cumraíocht na gcolún:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má chumasaítear é, athchóireofar cumraíocht na gcolún den radharc torthaí ón "
"seisiún roimhe seo nuair a osclaíonn tú fuinneog FSearch. Áirítear leis seo "
"méid agus infheictheacht na gcolún go léir."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1029
msgid ""
"<b>Remember sort order:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the sort order of the results view from the previous session "
"will be restored when you open an FSearch window."
msgstr ""
"<b>Meabhraigh ord sórtála:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, athchóireofar ord sórtála an radhairc torthaí ón "
"seisiún roimhe seo nuair a osclaíonn tú fuinneog FSearch."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1046
msgid ""
"<b>Open path with double click in path column:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, double clicking in the path column will open the selected path."
msgstr ""
"<b>Oscail an cosán le cliceáil faoi dhó sa cholún cosáin:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Más cumasaithe é, osclófar an cosán roghnaithe trí chliceáil faoi dhó sa "
"cholún cosáin."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1063
msgid ""
"<b>Single click to open:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, a single click will open the selected file/folder. If you only "
"want to select a file/folder while this setting is active, you need to hold "
"<i>Ctrl</i> at the same time while clicking the file/folder."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cliceáil amháin le hoscailt:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, osclófar an comhad/fillteán roghnaithe le cliceáil "
"amháin. Más mian leat comhad/fillteán amháin a roghnú agus an socrú seo "
"gníomhach, ní mór duit <i>Ctrl</i> a choinneáil síos ag an am céanna agus tú "
"ag cliceáil ar an gcomhad/fillteán."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1080
msgid ""
"<b>Show database indexing status:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the path that is currently being indexed is displayed in the "
"statusbar."
msgstr ""
"<b>Taispeáin stádas innéacsú bunachar sonraí:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, taispeántar an cosán atá á innéacsú faoi láthair sa "
"bharra stádais."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1097
msgid ""
"<b>Show warning dialogs:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, a warning dialog is displayed when a file or folder failed to "
"open."
msgstr ""
"<b>Taispeáin dialóga rabhaidh:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, taispeántar dialóg rabhaidh nuair a theip ar chomhad nó "
"fillteán a oscailt."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1114
msgid ""
"<b>Search in path when query contains path separators:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, search terms containing path separators (i.e. \"/\") will be "
"automatically matched against the full path of a file or folder."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuardaigh sa chonair nuair a bhíonn deighilteoirí cosáin san iarratas:</b>"
"\n"
"\n"
"Má chumasaítear é, déanfar téarmaí cuardaigh ina bhfuil deighilteoirí cosáin "
"(i.e. \"/\") a mheaitseáil go huathoibríoch i gcoinne chonair iomlán comhaid "
"nó fillteáin."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1131
msgid ""
"<b>Match case when query contains at least one upper case character:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, search terms containing at least one upper case character will "
"trigger a case-sensitive search. This means a search term like <i>Foo</i> "
"will match <i>FooBar.txt</i> but not <i>foobar.txt</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Meaitseáil cás nuair a bhíonn carachtar mór amháin ar a laghad sa "
"cheist:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má chumasaítear é, spreagfaidh téarmaí cuardaigh ina bhfuil carachtar mór "
"amháin ar a laghad cuardach íogair ó thaobh cás de. Ciallaíonn sé seo go "
"mbeidh téarma cuardaigh cosúil le <i>Foo</i> comhoiriúnach le <i>FooBar.txt</"
"i> ach ní le <i>foobar.txt</i>."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1148
msgid ""
"<b>Hide results when search is empty:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, no search results are displayed when the search entry is empty.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, all files and folders will be displayed when the search entry "
"is empty."
msgstr ""
"<b>Torthaí a cheilt nuair a bhíonn an cuardach folamh:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Más cumasaithe é, ní thaispeántar aon torthaí cuardaigh nuair a bhíonn an "
"iontráil chuardaigh folamh.\n"
"\n"
"Más díchumasaithe é, taispeánfar gach comhad agus fillteán nuair a bhíonn an "
"iontráil chuardaigh folamh."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1167
msgid ""
"<b>Search as you type:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search is automatically updated with every keystroke.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, the search is only updated when you hit <i>Enter</i> or press "
"the search button. "
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuardaigh agus tú ag clóscríobh:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Más cumasaithe é, déantar an cuardach a nuashonrú go huathoibríoch le gach "
"brú eochrach.\n"
"\n"
"Más díchumasaithe é, ní dhéantar an cuardach a nuashonrú ach amháin nuair a "
"bhuaileann tú <i>Iontráil</i> nó nuair a bhrúnn tú an cnaipe cuardaigh. "

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1186
msgid ""
"<b>Update database on start:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the database will be updated automatically in the background "
"when you start FSearch."
msgstr ""
"<b>Nuashonraigh bunachar sonraí ag an tús:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, déanfar an bunachar sonraí a nuashonrú go huathoibríoch "
"sa chúlra nuair a thosaíonn tú FSearch."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1203
msgid ""
"<b>Included folders:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This list contains all folders you want to include in the database.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Active:</b> If enabled, the path will included in the database to be "
"searched in.\n"
"\t• <b>Path:</b> The full path to be included.\n"
"\t• <b>One Filesystem:</b> If enabled, FSearch won't cross filesystem "
"boundaries for this folder"
msgstr ""
"<b>Fillteáin san áireamh:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Tá na fillteáin uile is mian leat a chur san áireamh sa bhunachar sonraí sa "
"liosta seo.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Gníomhach:</b> Má tá sé cumasaithe, cuirfear an cosán san áireamh sa "
"bhunachar sonraí le cuardach a dhéanamh ann.\n"
"\t• <b>Cosán:</b> An cosán iomlán le cur san áireamh.\n"
"\t• <b>Córas Comhad amháin:</b> Má tá sé cumasaithe, ní thrasnóidh FSearch "
"teorainneacha córas comhad don fhillteán seo"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1224
msgid ""
"<b>Add folder to database:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can select a folder you want to include "
"in the database for searching."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuir fillteán leis an mbunachar sonraí:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Osclaíonn an cnaipe seo dialóg inar féidir leat fillteán a roghnú ar mhaith "
"leat a chur san áireamh sa bhunachar sonraí le haghaidh cuardaigh."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1241
msgid ""
"<b>Add a specific path:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Type the full path of a folder here and click the button next to it to "
"include that folder in the database. This is useful for adding a path "
"directly without browsing for it."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuir cosán sonrach leis:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Clóscríobh cosán iomlán fillteáin anseo agus cliceáil an cnaipe in aice leis "
"chun an fillteán sin a chur san áireamh sa bhunachar sonraí. Tá sé seo "
"úsáideach chun cosán a chur leis go díreach gan brabhsáil dó."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1258
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected row:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This removes the selected folder from the list of included folders."
msgstr ""
"<b>Bain an ró roghnaithe:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Baintear an fillteán roghnaithe as an liosta fillteán atá san áireamh leis "
"seo."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1275
msgid ""
"<b>Attempt to monitor:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch watches this folder for changes and keeps the database "
"up to date automatically, so you don't have to rescan manually.\n"
"\n"
"Monitoring isn't supported on every file system and uses a small amount of "
"system resources per watched folder. For large directory trees with many "
"files the system may run out of resources to watch them all."
msgstr ""
"<b>Iarracht monatóireacht a dhéanamh:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, déanann FSearch faire ar an bhfillteán seo le haghaidh "
"athruithe agus coinníonn sé an bunachar sonraí cothrom le dáta go "
"huathoibríoch, mar sin ní gá duit athscanadh de láimh.\n"
"\n"
"Ní thacaítear le monatóireacht ar gach córas comhad agus úsáideann sé méid "
"beag acmhainní córais in aghaidh an fhillteáin faire. I gcás crainn eolaire "
"móra ina bhfuil go leor comhad, d'fhéadfadh go mbeadh ganntanas acmhainní ag "
"an gcóras chun faire orthu go léir."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1294
msgid ""
"<b>Scan after launch:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, this folder is rescanned every time FSearch starts, so the "
"database reflects any changes made while FSearch wasn't running."
msgstr ""
"<b>Scanadh tar éis lainseála:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, déantar an fillteán seo a athscanadh gach uair a "
"thosaíonn FSearch, ionas go léireofar sa bhunachar sonraí aon athruithe a "
"rinneadh agus FSearch gan a bheith ag rith."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1311
msgid ""
"<b>Stay on one file system:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch won't cross file system boundaries while scanning this "
"folder. Mounted file systems below it (e.g. external drives or network "
"shares) are skipped."
msgstr ""
"<b>Fan ar chóras comhad amháin:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, ní rachaidh FSearch trasna teorainneacha córas comhad "
"agus an fillteán seo á scanadh. Déantar neamhaird ar chórais chomhad atá "
"suite faoi (m.sh. tiomántáin sheachtracha nó scaireanna líonra)."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1328
msgid ""
"<b>Rescan every:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, this folder is rescanned automatically at the given interval. "
"Use the hours and minutes fields to set how often the rescan happens.\n"
"\n"
"This is useful for folders on file systems that can't be monitored for "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"<b>Athscanadh gach:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má chumasaítear é, déantar an fillteán seo a athscanadh go huathoibríoch ag "
"an eatramh tugtha. Úsáid na réimsí uaireanta agus nóiméad chun a shocrú cé "
"chomh minic a tharlaíonn an t-athscanadh.\n"
"\n"
"Tá sé seo úsáideach do fhillteáin ar chórais chomhad nach féidir "
"monatóireacht a dhéanamh orthu le haghaidh athruithe."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1347
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude rules:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This list contains rules for the files and folders you want to exclude from "
"the database.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Active:</b> If enabled, the rule is applied and matching items are "
"excluded.\n"
"\t• <b>Pattern:</b> The text matched against each item, interpreted "
"according to the Type.\n"
"\t• <b>Type:</b> How the pattern is interpreted — <i>Literal</i> (exact "
"text), <i>Wildcard</i> (using * and ?) or <i>Regex</i> (a regular "
"expression).\n"
"\t• <b>Match:</b> Whether the pattern is matched against the item's <i>Full "
"Path</i> or only its <i>Basename</i> (the name without the path).\n"
"\t• <b>Applies To:</b> Whether the rule affects <i>Files</i>, <i>Folders</i> "
"or both."
msgstr ""
"<b>Rialacha eisiamh:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Tá rialacha sa liosta seo do na comhaid agus na fillteáin is mian leat a "
"eisiamh ón mbunachar sonraí.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Gníomhach:</b> Má tá sé cumasaithe, cuirtear an riail i bhfeidhm agus "
"eisiatar míreanna meaitseála.\n"
"\t• <b>Patrún:</b> An téacs a mheaitseáiltear i gcoinne gach míre, "
"léirmhínithe de réir an Chineáil.\n"
"\t• <b>Cineál:</b> Conas a léirmhínítear an patrún — <i>Literal</i> (téacs "
"cruinn), <i>Wildcard</i> (ag baint úsáide as * agus ?) nó <i>Regex</i> "
"(sloinnt rialta).\n"
"\t• <b>Meaitseáil:</b> Cibé acu a mheaitseáiltear an patrún i gcoinne <i>"
"Cosán Iomlán</i> na míre nó a <i>Bonnainm</i> amháin (an t-ainm gan an cosán)"
".\n"
"\t• <b>Baineann le:</b> Cibé acu a mbíonn tionchar ag an riail ar <i>"
"Chomhaid</i>, <i>Fillteáin</i> nó an dá cheann."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1370
msgid ""
"<b>Add exclude rule:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This adds a new, empty rule to the list. Edit its Pattern, Type, Match and "
"Applies To columns to control what gets excluded from the database."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuir riail eisiaimh leis:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Cuireann sé seo riail nua, folamh leis an liosta. Cuirtear a cholúin Patrún, "
"Cineál, Meaitseáil agus Baineann Leat in eagar chun rialú a dhéanamh ar a "
"bhfuil eisiata ón mbunachar sonraí."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1387
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected row:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This removes the selected rule from the list of exclude rules."
msgstr ""
"<b>Bain an tsraith roghnaithe:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Baintear an riail roghnaithe as an liosta rialacha eisiaimh leis seo."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1404
msgid ""
"<b>Restore default exclude rules:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button restores the default set of exclude rules.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ All rules which were created or edited by the user will be lost! ⚠"
msgstr ""
"<b>Athchóirigh rialacha eisiaimh réamhshocraithe:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Athchóiríonn an cnaipe seo an tacar réamhshocraithe rialacha eisiaimh.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ Caillfear gach riail a chruthaigh nó a chuir an t-úsáideoir in eagar! ⚠"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1423
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude files and folders from database:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This is a semi-colon separated list of files (or folders) you want to "
"exclude from the database. For example <i>.git;.cache;*.swp</i> will exclude "
"all files or folders which are called either <i>.git</i> or <i>.cache</i> or "
"end with <i>.swp</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Eisiaigh comhaid agus fillteáin ón mbunachar sonraí:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Is liosta de chomhaid (nó fillteáin) é seo atá scartha le leathstad agus ar "
"mhaith leat a eisiamh ón mbunachar sonraí. Mar shampla, eisióidh <i>"
".git;.cache;*.swp</i> gach comhad nó fillteán ar a dtugtar <i>.git</i> nó <i>"
".cache</i> nó a chríochnaíonn le <i>.swp</i>."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1440
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude hidden files and folders:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, hidden files and folders will be excluded from the database "
"<i>(i.e. all files or folders which start with a dot character)</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Eisiamh comhaid agus fillteáin fholaithe:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má chumasaítear é, eisiamhfar comhaid agus fillteáin fholaithe ón mbunachar "
"sonraí <i>(i.e. gach comhad nó fillteán a thosaíonn le ponc)</i>."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1457
msgid "Focus a setting to get a detailed description of what it does."
msgstr "Dírigh ar shocrú chun cur síos mionsonraithe a fháil ar a ndéanann sé."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1470
msgid ""
"<b>Periodically update database at a specific time interval:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled and as long as FSearch is running, the database will be updated "
"periodically with the given time interval.\n"
"\n"
"If you want to update the database in the background, even when FSearch is "
"not running, you should use tools like cron or systemd timers to "
"periodically trigger the update with:\n"
"\n"
"<i><tt>fsearch --update-database</tt></i>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Nuashonraigh an bunachar sonraí go tréimhsiúil ag eatramh ama ar leith:</"
"b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe agus fad a bheidh FSearch ag rith, déanfar an bunachar "
"sonraí a nuashonrú go tréimhsiúil leis an eatramh ama tugtha.\n"
"\n"
"Más mian leat an bunachar sonraí a nuashonrú sa chúlra, fiú nuair nach "
"bhfuil FSearch ag rith, ba chóir duit uirlisí cosúil le cron nó timers "
"systemd a úsáid chun an nuashonrú a spreagadh go tréimhsiúil le:\n"
"\n"
"<i><tt>fsearch --update-database</tt></i>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1491
msgid ""
"<b>Launch desktop files:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, activating a <i>.desktop</i> file will launch the application "
"defined within that file. This way FSearch can act like an application "
"launcher. Otherwise the <i>.desktop</i> file will be opened with the default "
"handler for this type of files, which is usually a text editor."
msgstr ""
"<b>Seoladh comhaid deisce:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Más cumasaithe é, seolfar an feidhmchlár atá sainithe sa chomhad sin nuair a "
"ghníomhaítear comhad <i>.desktop</i>. Ar an mbealach seo, is féidir le "
"FSearch gníomhú mar lainseálaí feidhmchláir. Seachas sin, osclófar an comhad "
"<i>.desktop</i> leis an láimhseálaí réamhshocraithe don chineál seo comhad, "
"arb é eagarthóir téacs de ghnáth é."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1508
msgid ""
"<b>Filters:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This is a list of all available filters. A filter is a predefined search.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Name:</b> A unique and descriptive identifier for the filter\n"
"\t• <b>Macro:</b> By typing the macro text followed by a ':' you can enable "
"the filter on demand\n"
"\t• <b>Query:</b> The search term by which the database should be filtered"
msgstr ""
"<b>Scagairí:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Seo liosta de na scagairí go léir atá ar fáil. Is cuardach réamhshainithe é "
"scagaire.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Ainm:</b> Aitheantóir uathúil agus tuairisciúil don scagaire\n"
"\t• <b>Macra:</b> Trí théacs an mhacra a chlóscríobh agus ':' ina dhiaidh "
"sin is féidir leat an scagaire a chumasú ar iarratas\n"
"\t• <b>Iarratas:</b> An téarma cuardaigh lenar cheart an bunachar sonraí a "
"scagadh"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1529
msgid ""
"<b>Add a new filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can edit a new filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuir scagaire nua leis:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Osclaíonn an cnaipe seo dialóg inar féidir leat scagaire nua a chur in eagar."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1546
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button removes the currently selected filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Bain an scagaire roghnaithe:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Baintear an scagaire atá roghnaithe faoi láthair leis an gcnaipe seo."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1563
msgid ""
"<b>Edit selected filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can edit the selected filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cuir an scagaire roghnaithe in eagar:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Osclaíonn an cnaipe seo dialóg inar féidir leat an scagaire roghnaithe a "
"chur in eagar."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1580
msgid ""
"<b>Restore default filters:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button restores the default filter configuration.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ All filters which were created or edited by the user will be lost! ⚠"
msgstr ""
"<b>Athchóirigh scagairí réamhshocraithe:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Athchóiríonn an cnaipe seo cumraíocht réamhshocraithe an scagaire.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ Caillfear gach scagaire a chruthaigh nó a chuir an t-úsáideoir in eagar! ⚠"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1599
msgid ""
"<b>Exit on Escape:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch exits when the Escape key is pressed instead of the "
"window being minimized."
msgstr ""
"<b>Imeacht ar Escape:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, scoireann FSearch nuair a bhrúitear an eochair Escape "
"seachas an fhuinneog a íoslaghdú."

